Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Join forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, everyone. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should cooperate together\Nso we can achieve our goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You all want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become Mom of this House.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to drag Isabella down\Nfrom her position as Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and seize that position for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's position?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to clarify, those are my true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to break free from this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about\Nthe management system here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girls who fulfill certain conditions\Nand live until 12 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are presented with two paths\Nwhen they're about to be shipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To continue and die,\Nor aim to become a Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are the conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scores above a certain number\Nand the Mom's recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can meet these two requirements,\Nyou can survive without escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- If you're a girl.\N- A girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your body will never be able to leave this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chip inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If an adult steps one foot outside of the farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,an electrical current will be sent through this\Nand their heart will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time,\Nif something else makes their heart stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then it acts as a transmitter\Nthat notifies the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we couldn't kill the adults after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can only live inside the farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to live\Nthe best possible life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a Mom.\NEven if it's fake, it's a life for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But to get that, Isabella is in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you all escape, she will be blamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Escape. That will become a benefit for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to ship us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cooperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me verify one thing with Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your guarantee\Nthat you won't betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Ray tells this to Mom, you can crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I tell Mom that Ray's been a double agent,\NI can crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why neither of us will betray the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also share any other information\Nthat only I know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's proof of my friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come to my room tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to live the best possible life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was even one of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't care at all about\Nthe lives of us children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she said she won't ship us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that she won't. She can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she really wanted us to escape, she just needs\Nto assist us quietly when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's showing us her cards only because\Nshe wants to gain our trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she want our trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She wants evidence that shows our rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's in a position\Nwhere the higher-ups
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,won't trust her without reliable evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Mom, she doesn't have\Nthe authority to ship us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what if she finds\Nthe rope we hid in the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. We can say various excuses\Nto explain the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like we were going to use it to play with. But—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed if she finds the equipment\Nthat breaks the tracking devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's reliable evidence\Nthat we can't make excuses for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NI won't make that kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we have her believe that we don't know where\Nthe tracking devices are, or how to break it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sister would believe us\Nif we play the cards correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're dealing with that Sister Krone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds nice that she'll tell us\Nanything we want to know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, why do we have to\Njoin forces with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it give us an advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we use her well,\Nwe might obtain some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's one less person getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can focus on investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to use every opportunity we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to discuss the steps\Nfor the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?\NGo ahead. Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Whether it be about the farm\Nor about the headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show us that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tool that receives the signal\Nfrom our tracking devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Doesn't it look simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It only shows the current location\Nbut can't specify who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew about the tracking devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mom showed us once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know where it is\Nor how to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They're located in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The left ear. Around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to break them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if it breaks, it sends out a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To that thing, and also to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to take it out. Or cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there are no decent blades in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a scalpel. For medical use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're outside, there's no medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we escape, I don't want\Nto take risks with blood loss or infections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The infirmary is equipped\Nwith medicine and tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anesthesia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think there's enough for five kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also teach you how to use them,\Nand I'll lend you the key to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's settled. Okay, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, how old are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you livestock ever since you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How rude to ask a grown woman her age...\NIs what I'd like to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 26. Born and raised at Grace Field.\NJust not here at Plant Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Isabella is 31.\NThat's what I saw in the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the outside? You've seen it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you think I would say yes,\Neven if it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there are humans outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your food is made\Nby the higher-ups and us adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there are humans from the outside\Nwho bring your clothes and other supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw them at the headquarters once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those humans have equal standing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are humans outside\Nwho haven't been eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get mixed in with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't know how long\Nthe demons have been around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Demons? Oh, you're talking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you know how\Nthe world came to be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this House located?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the security of this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know about that. There isn't much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They rely on the tracking devices,\Nso they don't have many guards posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they don't even patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you already knew the location\Nof the tracking devices and how to break them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand a lot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just words that provide information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans give away a lot of information\Njust by standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attitude. Gaze. Blinking.\NSweat. Gestures. Pupils. Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of these are hints\Nto find out what you're really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet for you two, even though I said\Nthe tracking device was in your ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't touch them to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The arrangements to get them out were made,\Nbut you didn't look happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you ask about\Nthe tracking devices when it wasn't necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you want to hide from me?\NAre you keeping a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, right? Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the next time you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk much more than we did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing shown at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So your last reward is a camera, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was interested\Nin the phenomenon of photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've only seen\Nphotographs and cameras in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to get greedy,\NI would have wanted to develop them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really looks like\Nyou cut out a moment in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that matter,\Nis it okay if it's after lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we start free time after lunch,\NI'll distract Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman and Emma will climb the wall\Nto inspect the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don and Gilda, stay outside where you can see\Nthe south window on the house's second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case I fail to distract Mom,\NI'll signal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Emma and Norman know\Nto cancel the inspection immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have six days until the escape, but at least\Nuntil January, we have two and a half months
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,until it's time for me to be shipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if something happens,\Nimmediately cancel the inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything needs to be done secretly.\NWe need to pretend to be controllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gilda, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Ready for some tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister found out\Nthat we can break the tracking devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to move up the escape day.\NWhen can you break the tracking devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I have all the necessary parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can break them anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is really a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will we break the tracking devices\Nand escape first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or will Sister find this evidence first\Nand turn us in before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've taken care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I wonder why\Nthey pretended not to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They knew the location\Nand how to break the tracking devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did they find out in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, how will they break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will they use a special tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could they have made such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then would that happen to be\Nthe reliable evidence I need?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why they were scared and lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then it's time for a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you put out the plates?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm so hungry.\N- Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cleaning the floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you get the forks?\N- Can you help me here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. This really is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got it unexpectedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isabella's second weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how should I go about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I show this note and appeal to Grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can oust Isabella\Nand obtain the Mom's position?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can ship out the brats\Nunconditionally, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how... how does Ray know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even Isabella shouldn't know about this\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the headquarters. You should open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
